      • enteredVENULocation

        public void enteredVENULocation(int serviceNumber,
                                int locationId,
                                double distance,
                                boolean initial)

        Callback when the phone is within range of a location that matches the Brand ID.

        Parameters:
        serviceNumber - Assigned service number to the phone.
        locationId - ID of brand location.
        distance - Distance from source of location broadcasting in meters
        initial - True when entering for the first time. Subsequent calls will be false
